{
  "stem": "935.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When they got tired of playing games, this-- the Germans summoned 500 bombers, bombed Rotterdam, flattening it completely, and then, you know, moved in with the invasion-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They fought for five days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, even so, they didn't stand a prayer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a group of incredible brave men who fought and fought and fought, knowing it is suicide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they fought in spite of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, and then they were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And something very strange happened with that whole country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It became so quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You didn't see anyone on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You didn't see anyone anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "All the windows were shut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The doors were shut.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was like the whole country had stopped breathing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was like it was in mourning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was already in mourning of what was yet to come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I lived very close with a tenor and his lady friend and a comedian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were very close together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And after the first five days and you're kind of, you know-- got back a little bit you to reality.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You decided something has to happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You didn't know what would-- what would happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We had nothing to compare it with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We didn't have another country where they said, this is, this is going to happen now to the Jews or to this-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "All we knew is that we still have the power to decide something for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we-- this small group, the friends, the tenor, and his lady friend, and the comedian, and I-- decided we want to try to get to England, which was not crazy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because from the coast, there are a lot of little shipping boats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And you can see, practically, on a clear day, see Dover.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
